{"id":656990,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/10/【对比新闻】保障妇女权益必须上升为国家意志/","date":"2020-10-02T09:50:03Z","modified":"2020-10-02T10:02:26Z","title":"【对比新闻】“保障妇女权益必须上升为国家意志” VS  “拉姆法案话题被封了”","content":"<p>10月1日，国家主席习近平在联合国大会纪念北京世界妇女大会25周年高级别会议上通过视频发表讲话，强调保障<a href=\"https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_9445751\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">妇女权益必须上升为国家意志</a>。</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-656992\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"auto\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/1.jpg 828w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/1-271x300.jpg 271w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/1-768x849.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 828px) 100vw, 828px\" /></p>\n<p>但就在前一天（9月30日），腾讯新闻旗下的谷雨工作室刊发报道<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/10/%e8%b0%b7%e9%9b%a8%e5%ae%9e%e9%aa%8c%e5%ae%a4%ef%bd%9c%e8%a2%ab%e5%89%8d%e5%a4%ab%e7%83%a7%e6%af%81%e7%9a%84%e6%8b%89%e5%a7%86/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">《被前夫烧毁的拉姆》</a>，讲述了视频主播拉姆被长期家暴，但在多次报警后仍未得到保护，最后在9月14日时被前夫泼汽油后纵火烧死的事件。</p>\n<p>报道发出后引发巨大反响，不少网友以“拉姆法案”为标签，呼吁对警方面对家暴时的不作为进行惩罚。</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-656996\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/47ye2m1j1jq51-1024x870.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"auto\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/47ye2m1j1jq51-1024x870.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/47ye2m1j1jq51-300x255.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/47ye2m1j1jq51-768x653.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/47ye2m1j1jq51.png 1071w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></p>\n<p>但就在不到一天的时间里，“拉姆法案”10月2日已在中国被全网封杀。</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-656999\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/22-1.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"auto\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/22-1.jpeg 828w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/22-1-300x242.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/22-1-768x619.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 828px) 100vw, 828px\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-657002\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/huncma3l1jq51-1024x830.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"auto\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/huncma3l1jq51-1024x830.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/huncma3l1jq51-300x243.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/huncma3l1jq51-768x623.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/huncma3l1jq51.png 1067w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></p>\n","author":1070,"categories":[18271,41492,38912,41420],"tags":[42121,18979,42117,42118]}